ca.mcgill.ecse211.model

Class ReturnHome

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse211.model.ReturnHome

  • public class ReturnHome
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles the robot's navigation from the search zone (i.e., search zone lower left corner or search zone upper right corner) to the staring corner. It also handles the off-loading of the cans in the starting corner.
    Author:
    Carlo D'Angelo
